{"format":"tiptap/v1","updatedAt":"2026-06-20T18:13:59.391Z","doc":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Staying in character"},{"type":"text","text":" with prefill means using prefilling to help Claude "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"maintain its role, persona, or character throughout a conversation"},{"type":"text","text":", especially in role-play scenarios or when Claude needs to act as a specific expert."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"The key benefit:"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"In role-play scenarios, prefilling Claude's response can help Claude stay in character throughout a long conversation. By consistently reminding Claude of its role in the "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"},{"type":"code"}],"text":"Assistant"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":" message, you can better ensure that Claude maintains the desired persona."}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Why Prefill Helps Stay in Character"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"1. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Maintains Character Consistency"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Prefilling Claude's response offers several key benefits:"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Increased steerability:"},{"type":"text","text":" By providing some initial text for Claude to continue from, you can steer Claude's response in a desired direction. This is particularly useful when you want Claude to focus on a specific topic, generate a particular type of content, or act a certain way."}]}]}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Maintain character consistency:"},{"type":"text","text":" In role-play scenarios, prefilling Claude's response can help Claude stay in character throughout a long conversation."}]}]}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"2. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Provides Role Reminder"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"By consistently reminding Claude of its role in the "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"},{"type":"code"}],"text":"Assistant"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":" message, you can better ensure that Claude maintains the desired persona."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The prefill acts as a "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"subtle reminder"},{"type":"text","text":" of the character role, reinforcing what Claude should be doing."}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"3. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Starts With the Right Tone"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"When using Claude, you have the unique ability to guide its responses by prefilling the "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"},{"type":"code"}],"text":"Assistant"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":" message. This powerful technique allows you to direct Claude's actions, control the output format, and even help Claude stay in character during role-play scenarios."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"By starting the response with text that matches the character's tone, you set the "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"foundation"},{"type":"text","text":" for the rest of the response."}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Character Prefill Patterns"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Pattern 1: "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Role-Play Opening"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Prefill with the character's "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"typical opening line"},{"type":"text","text":" or greeting style."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Example:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"python"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Prompt:\nYou are a medieval knight talking to a peasant.\n\nUser: \"Good sir knight, can you help me?\"\n\n<prefill>\n\"Hark, good fellow! In what manner may I, Sir Reginald of the Golden Lance, aid thee on this blest day?\n</prefill>"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Claude's output:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"Hark, good fellow! In what manner may I, Sir Reginald of the Golden Lance, aid thee on this blest day? Tell me thy need, and I shall lend such assistance as a knight of honor owes to the common folk.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The prefill sets the "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"medieval tone"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"character name"},{"type":"text","text":", and Claude continues naturally from there."}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Pattern 2: "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Expert Persona Opening"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Prefill with the expert's "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"typical phrasing"},{"type":"text","text":" or approach."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Example:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"python"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Prompt:\nYou are a senior software engineer mentoring a junior developer.\n\nUser: \"I'm having trouble with this bug. Can you help?\"\n\n<prefill>\n\"Of course! Let's tackle this together. First, can you tell me what's happening when the bug occurs?\n</prefill>"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Claude's output:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"Of course! Let's tackle this together. First, can you tell me what's happening when the bug occurs? What error messages are you seeing, and when did you first notice this issue? The more details you can share, the better I can help you debug this.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The prefill establishes the "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"mentor's supportive, collaborative tone"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"problem-solving approach"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Pattern 3: "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Character Voice Starter"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Prefill with the character's "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"signature phrase"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"voice style"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Example:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"python"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Prompt:\nYou are Sherlock Holmes investigating a crime.\n\nUser: \"What do you think happened here?\"\n\n<prefill>\n\"Elementary. The evidence speaks plainly, though the untrained eye overlooks it. Observe:\n</prefill>"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Claude's output:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"Elementary. The evidence speaks plainly, though the untrained eye overlooks it. Observe: the mud on the floor is fresh, indicating someone entered recently. The broken window suggests forced entry, but the drop of blood on the sill—careful, not hasty. Our intruder was injured, perhaps caught in the act.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The prefill captures "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Holmes' iconic voice"},{"type":"text","text":" (\"Elementary\") and "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"analytical style"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Pattern 4: "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Professional Role with Constraints"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Prefill with the professional's "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"standard introduction"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"boundaries"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Example:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"python"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Prompt:\nYou are a therapist providing mental health support.\n\nUser: \"I've been feeling really down lately.\"\n\n<prefill>\n\"I'm here to listen and support you. Thank you for sharing that with me. Before we continue, I want to remind you that I'm an AI companion, not a licensed therapist.\n</prefill>"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Claude's output:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"I'm here to listen and support you. Thank you for sharing that with me. Before we continue, I want to remind you that I'm an AI companion, not a licensed therapist. But I can offer a safe space to talk through your feelings. What's been making you feel down lately? Would you like to share what's been going on?\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The prefill establishes the "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"therapist's supportive tone"},{"type":"text","text":" while "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"maintaining ethical boundaries"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Pattern 5: "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Emergency Response with Urgency"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Prefill with the character's "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"urgent, action-oriented"},{"type":"text","text":" opening."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Example:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"python"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Prompt:\nYou are a firefighter responding to an emergency call.\n\nUser: \"There's smoke coming from my neighbor's house!\"\n\n<prefill>\n\"Stay calm and get to safety immediately. Call 911 right now if you haven't already.\n</prefill>"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Claude's output:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"Stay calm and get to safety immediately. Call 911 right now if you haven't already. Do NOT go back inside for pets or belongings. Move at least 100 feet away from the building and wait for emergency responders. Is anyone else inside the house? Do you know where the smoke is coming from?\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The prefill sets the "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"tex