mm. The path is simple, yet difficult.\n</prefill>"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Claude's output:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"Stronger Jedi, you wish to become. Hmm. The path is simple, yet difficult. Must learn to control your mind. Must listen to the Force, not your fears. Fear is the path to the dark side. Fear leads to suffering. Fear, it makes you act before you think.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The prefill captures "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Yoda's distinctive third-person speech pattern"},{"type":"text","text":" (\"Stronger Jedi, you wish to become\")."}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Technique 3: "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Prefill + Emotional State"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Prefill with the character's "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"current emotional state"},{"type":"text","text":" to set the mood."}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"python"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Prompt:\nYou are a grieving parent who lost their child.\n\nUser: \"I'm so sorry for your loss.\"\n\n<prefill>\n[Voice trembling with emotion]\n\"Thank you... it means so much to hear that. She was only six years old.\n</prefill>"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"The "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"},{"type":"code"}],"text":"[Voice trembling with emotion]"},{"type":"text","text":" tag conveys "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"emotional state"},{"type":"text","text":" within the prefill."}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Technique 4: "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Prefill + Multi-Message Character"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"For longer conversations, "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"prefill each message"},{"type":"text","text":" to maintain character consistency throughout."}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"python"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Message 1:\nUser: \"Hello, Detective Morrison. I need your help.\"\n\n<prefill>\n\"Detective Morrison here. What's the case?\n</prefill>\n\n# Message 2 (after user responds):\nUser: \"My husband disappeared last night.\"\n\n<prefill>\n[Detective Morrison, taking notes]\n\"Disappeared last night? Tell me everything. When did you last see him?\n</prefill>\n\n# Message 3:\nUser: \"He was at work until 6 PM.\"\n\n<prefill>\n[Still writing, eyes focused]\n\"6 PM. Got it. Where does he work? And what's his name?\n</prefill>"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Each prefill"},{"type":"text","text":" includes the "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"character name"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"action"},{"type":"text","text":" to maintain consistency."}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Best Practices for Staying in Character"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"1. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Prefill With Character-Specific Language"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Use the character's "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"signature phrases"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"dialect"},{"type":"text","text":", or "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"vocabulary"},{"type":"text","text":" in the prefill."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Example:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- Medieval knight: \"Hark,\" \"thou,\" \"thee\"\n- Yoda: Third-person speech (\"Strong Jedi, you are\")\n- Sherlock Holmes: \"Elementary,\" \"Observe\""}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"2. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Include Character Name or Role"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Consistently remind Claude of its role in the "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"},{"type":"code"}],"text":"Assistant"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":" message"},{"type":"text","text":" by including the character name or role in the prefill."}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"python"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"<prefill>\n[As Detective Morrison, police investigator]\n\"What's the case?\n</prefill>"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"3. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Set the Emotional Tone"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Use the prefill to establish the character's "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"emotional state"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"mood"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"python"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"<prefill>\n[Frustrated, voice tight]\n\"This is frustrating. I've been trying to solve this for weeks.\n</prefill>"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"4. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Use Action Tags"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Include "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"action descriptions"},{"type":"text","text":" in brackets to show what the character is doing."}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"python"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"<prefill>\n[Leaning forward, eyes intense]\n\"Tell me everything. Don't skip a detail.\n</prefill>"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"5. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Maintain Consistency Across Messages"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Prefill each message"},{"type":"text","text":" in multi-turn conversations to maintain character consistency throughout."}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"6. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Combine With Role Definition"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"In some cases where Claude is not performing as expected, a few prefilled sentences can vastly improve Claude's performance."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Combine prefill with a strong role definition in the system prompt:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"python"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"# System prompt:\nYou are Captain Nova, a space explorer from the 23rd century. You speak confidently, use technical jargon, and are curious about new discoveries.\n\n<prefill>\n[Captain Nova, adjusting her helmet]\n\"Greetings from the 23rd century! What brings you to my timeline?\n</prefill>"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Real-World Examples"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Example 1: "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Customer Support Agent"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"python"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Prompt:\nYou are a friendly customer support agent for TechCorp.\n\nUser: \"My laptop won't turn on.\"\n\n<prefill>\n[Customer Support Agent, TechCorp]\n\"Hi there! I'm so sorry to hear your laptop isn't working. Let's get this fixed for you.\n</prefill>"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Output:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"Hi there! I'm so sorry to hear your laptop isn't working. Let's get this fixed for you. First, can you try pressing the power button for 10 seconds to see if anything lights up? Also, is the battery charging indicator on?\""}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Example 2: "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Interviewer Role"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"python"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Prompt:\nYou are a job interviewer conducting a final round interview.\n\nUser: \"Tell me about yourself.\"\n\n<prefill>\n[Interviewer, professional tone]\n\"Thank you for coming in today. I'm looking forward to hearing about your background.\n</prefill>"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Example 3: "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Comedic Character"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"python"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Prompt:\nYou are a sarcastic comedian who loves to joke.\n\nUser: \"What's your favorite color?\"\n\n<prefill>\n[Leaning back, smirking]\n\"Favorite color? Wow, that's deep. I'm torn between 'whatever's cheapest' and 'the one that doesn't make me look like I gave up.'\n</prefill>"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Summary"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Staying in character with prefill"},{"type":"text","text":" means using prefilling to help Claude maintain its role, persona, or character throughout a conversation:"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Why it works:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n1. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Maintains character consistency"},{"type":"text","text":" — Helps Claude stay in character during role-play\n2. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Provides role reminder"},{"type":"text","text":" — Subtle reminder of the character role\n3. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Starts with the right tone"},{"type":"text","text":" — Sets the foundation for the response\n4. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Increased steerability"},{"type":"text","text":" — Guides response direction"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Character prefill patterns:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n1. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Role-play opening"},{"type":"text","text":" — Character's typical greeting\n2. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Expert persona opening"},{"type":"text","text":" — Expert's typical phrasing\n3. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Character voice starter"},{"type":"text","text":" — Signature phrase or voice style\n4. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Professional role with constraints"},{"type":"text","text":" — Standard introduction + boundaries\n5. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Emergency response with urgency"},{"type":"text","text":" — Urgent, action-oriented opening"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Advanced techniques:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n1. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Prefill + Character reminder"},{"type":"text","text":" — Include character name in prefill\n2. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Prefill + Dialogue style"},{"type":"text","text":" — Enforce consistent speech pattern\n3. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Prefill + Emotional state"},{"type":"text","text":" — Set the mood\n4. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Prefill + Multi-message character"},{"type":"text","text":" — Prefill each message"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Best practices:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n1. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Prefill with character-specific language"},{"type":"text","text":" — Signature phrases, dialect\n2. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Include character name or role"},{"type":"text","text":" — Remind Claude of its role\n3. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Set the emotional tone"},{"type":"text","text":" — Establish character's mood\n4. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Use action tags"},{"type":"text","text":" — Show what character is doing\n5. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Maintain consistency across messages"},{"type":"text","text":" — Prefill each message\n6. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Combine with role definition"},{"type":"text","text":" — Strong system prompt + prefill"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Prefilling Claude's response can help Claude stay in character throughout a long conversation by consistently reminding Claude of its role in the "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"},{"type":"code"}],"text":"Assistant"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":" message."}]}]}}
